title: Options data reveal where Intel stock will be trading after earnings on Jan 22

title: By 2027, This Could Be One of the Most Important Stocks in Its Industry
text: TSMC dominates the contract chip manufacturing market, and its foundry capabilities are crucial to global tech supply chains. Geopolitical dynamics could result in Intel quickly gaining share in the foundry market.
